Set date/time - DHCP Server 

        configure 
        sntp unicast 
        sntp 30 
        sntp server priority 1 192.168.204.254 
        ip timep dhcp interval 1 
        time timezone 600 
        time daylight-time-rule user-defined begin 1 Sun Oct 2:00 end 1 Sun Apr 3:00 offset 60 
        timesync sntp 
        write memory 
        show time 
        show sntp  
